data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This magnificent 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom gem with a finished basement boasts approximately 5000 sq ft of pure luxury. As you step into the entry foyer, you'll be greeted by the elegance of designer hardwood flooring and impeccable finishes that will leave you in awe.    The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring stained cabinets, solid counters, and a spacious island that beckons culinary adventures. Whether you're hosting a formal dinner in the dining room that comfortably seats 8+ or enjoying a cozy evening in the formal living room, this home is designed for seamless entertaining.    Retreat to the master suite, where you'll find a sitting area, trey ceilings, an oversize closet, and a spa-like bathroom with double vanity, a garden tub, and a separate shower – your private sanctuary awaits.    The basement level offers an additional bedroom and bathroom, along with bonus rooms that can adapt to your needs – perfect for guests, a home office, or a media room.     Nestled on a HUGE LOT, this property backs up to a serene wooded area, providing a sense of tranquility and privacy that's hard to find. With too many exceptional features to list, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make it yours!
